{"id":6994,"date":"2018-10-31T11:28:20","date_gmt":"2018-10-31T16:28:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/?p=6994"},"modified":"2023-10-11T13:22:27","modified_gmt":"2023-10-11T18:22:27","slug":"a-cascade-of-blades","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/features\/2018\/10\/31\/a-cascade-of-blades\/","title":{"rendered":"A Cascade of Blades"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many people find enjoyment in certain hobbies such as sports, reading, music, and art. Other hobbies can consist of traveling or collecting certain items. Some common items to collect are toys, games and dolls. Freshman Ian Allen has found amusement in collecting different swords along with rocks and knives. He has been collecting swords for five years now.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are many different sizes and kinds of swords to collect. One also has to be cautious when collecting items such as swords and knives because they are weapons and are therefore regulated by the state.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cSwords have fascinated me for a while,\u201d Allen said. \u201cI don\u2019t know why, it\u2019s just fun to me. It\u2019s my sort of entertainment.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Acquiring a sword is not as difficult as one may think it to be. Allen buys some of his swords from Ebay and Wish online, but his father knows of other places for Allen to obtain swords.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cMy dad works at U-Haul so he knows dealers there. He knows some metalsmiths and that\u2019s where I usually get them,\u201d Allen said.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Allen\u2019s collection consists of seven swords altogether. Each of his swords have some unique quality about them.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cI have one katana, one old-school, like knights and armor,\u201d Allen said, \u201cand then I have one sword that can split into two, and one that has a hidden blade.\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These swords, which Allen displays in his closet, can be used as dangerous weapons, so he offers some advice.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cBe safe,\u201d Allen said.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-7106\" src=\"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed-356x475.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"356\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed-356x475.jpg 356w, https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed-675x900.jpg 675w, https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed-300x400.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/unnamed.jpg 1126w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 356px) 100vw, 356px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Many people find enjoyment in certain hobbies such as sports, reading, music, and art. Other hobbies can consist of traveling or collecting certain items. Some common items to collect are toys, games and dolls. Freshman Ian Allen has found amusement in collecting different swords along with rocks and knives. He has been collecting swords for&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":76,"featured_media":7105,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6994"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/